{% endif %}
<ul class="fit-andfill-list">
<li>{{styleName}} run true to size.</li>
<li>If between sizes, use our easy <a href="javascript:;" class="size_chart" data-fancybox data-src="#size-chart{{product.id}}" data-type="inline" data-no-instant><strong>Size Guide</strong></a> to see whether to size up or down.</li>
